snippet.title: Disney TSUM TSUM Festival - Release Date Trailer - SWITCH
snippet.description:
The super cute Tsum Tsum will make their way to Nintendo Switch on 8 November! Get a glimpse of the many party games featured in Disney TSUM TSUM FESTIVAL and get ready for hours of fun with friends and family! 

#TsumTsumFest
